Title: Brown Hearted
Plot: The Celebrity Frontiers escapade has made Jaquie hot property and she is quickly courted by a powerful agent named Maureen Grigg. Kim feels betrayed, having just quit her job to start her own agency which Jaquie was supposed to be a part of. When Maureen renegotiates Jaquie?s salary at the radio station and gets James fired in the process, Jaquie realizes she might not have made a very wise choice.
